  "2026-04-06T16:48:05.699Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence used pm context pm search and open or in-progress lists. Net-new scope under pm-o7be for activity filtering and automation stream behavior.
  "2026-04-06T18:25:50.309Z",codex-agent,"Implemented activity scaling controls: --id, --op, --author, --from, --to filters in runActivity with deterministic descending sort preserved and inclusive-from/exclusive-to window semantics. Added optional activity stream mode via --stream [rows|ndjson|jsonl] requiring --json, emitting meta/entry/end NDJSON rows for automation parity with list stream UX. Updated command wiring, contracts flags/aliases, shell completion, help examples, and Pi wrapper mapping (including stream + filter arguments). Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/calendar-command.spec.ts tests/unit/history-activity-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts (208/208 passed)."
